<HEAD>The Fir&s;t BOOK of Mon&s;ieur <HI>TAVERNER</HI>'s <HI>Per&s;ian</HI> Travels. Of the &s;everal Roads from <HI>Paris to &punc;&s;pahan</HI> the chief City of <HI>Per&s;ia,</HI> through the Northern Provinces of <HI>Turky.</HI></HEAD>
<LIST>
