<P><HI>Bo&s;t,</HI> 91 deg. 28 min. Long. 32 deg. 16 min. Lat. A great City, to which be|longs the faire&s;t and &s;tronge&s;t Ca&s;tle in all <HI>Per&s;ia.</HI></P>
<P><HI>Bourou-Jerd&eacute;,</HI> 74 deg. 30 min. Long. 34 deg. 20 min. Lat. Famous for Saffron, and for being the native City of many Learned Men.</P>
