<ROW>
<CELL>At <HI>Badelpoura</HI> it is, where the loaded Waggons pay th<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 letter"> duties of <HI>Brampour;</HI> but the Waggons that carry nothing but Pa&s;&s;engers pay nothing.</CELL>
