<CELL>The&s;e two la&s;t places are two Towns, where, as in all the Country round about, they make <HI>Indigo</HI>-Plate, which is round; and as it is the be&s;t of all the <HI>In|digo's,</HI> &s;o is it double the price.</CELL>
