<ROW>
<CELL><HI>Atek</HI> is a City &s;ituated upon a point of Land where two Rivers meet together. 'Tis one of the be&s;t and &s;tronge&s;t Garri&s;ons the Great <HI>Mogul</HI> has; into which there is no &s;tranger permitted to enter without a Pa&s;&s;port from the King. Father <HI>Roux</HI> the Je&s;uit and his Companion, going this way to <HI>I&s;pahan,</HI> and not having the King's Pa&s;&s;port, were forc'd to return back to <HI>Lahor,</HI> where they embark'd upon the River for <HI>Scimdi,</HI> from whence they pa&s;t into <HI>Per&s;ia.</HI></CELL>
